addBank(address,string).details: This function adds a Bank to the environment (list of banks)

addPerson(address,string,string,bool,uin.details: This function adds a Person to the environment (list of persons)

params.KYCstatus: Status of the KYC procedure of the person

addRegulator(address,string).details: This function adds a Regulator to the environment (list of regulators)

changeBalanceOfPerson(bool,address,uint2.details: This function changes the balance amount of a person

params.pay_receive: Decides if the person is paying money (true) or receiving money (false)

checkKYCstatusPerson(address).details: This function checkes the KYC status of a person

constructor.details: This constructor is used to initiate the actors needed to perform the two use-cases. Actors are linked with their addresses.

getPersonBalance(address).details: This function gets the balance amount of a person

getPersonName(address).details: This function gets the name of a person

initiateGlobalPaymentContract(address,ad.details: GLOBAL PAYMENT: This function initiates a GlobalPaymentContract

params.FX_rate: Exchange rate between the two currencies
params.transferamount: The transferamount of the global payment

receiveFunds(address).details: GLOBAL PAYMENT: This function receive the funds in the process of a global payment contract

setKYCstatusperson(address,bool).details: This function changes the KYC status of a person

params.status: New KYC status of the person

submitTransfer(address).details: GLOBAL PAYMENT: This function submits the transfer in the process of a global payment contract
